import React from 'react'
import { Document, Page, View, Text, StyleSheet, PDFViewer } from '@react-pdf/renderer'

function PDF(props) {
    return (
        <PDFViewer>
            <Document>
                <Page>
                    <View>
                        <Text>
                            Hello World!
                        </Text>
                    </View>
                </Page>
            </Document>
        </PDFViewer>
    )
}

export default PDF
